{"id":2613,"date":"2023-08-23T15:43:20","date_gmt":"2023-08-23T08:43:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2613"},"modified":"2023-09-20T10:46:35","modified_gmt":"2023-09-20T03:46:35","slug":"cac-buoc-xac-nhan-nhap-hoc-tren-cong-thong-tin-bo-giao-duc-va-dao-tao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/cac-buoc-xac-nhan-nhap-hoc-tren-cong-thong-tin-bo-giao-duc-va-dao-tao\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00c1C B\u01af\u1edaC X\u00c1C NH\u1eacN NH\u1eacP H\u1eccC TR\u00caN C\u1ed4NG TH\u00d4NG TIN B\u1ed8 GI\u00c1O D\u1ee4C V\u00c0 \u0110\u00c0O T\u1ea0O"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 th\u00ed sinh x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc n\u0103m 2023 ph\u1ea3i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng, th\u1eddi gian t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 22\/8 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 17 gi\u1edd 00 ng\u00e0y 06\/9\/2023<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, sau khi c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00fang tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc n\u0103m 2023, th\u00ed sinh c\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean c\u1ed5ng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc d\u00e0nh cho th\u00ed sinh. N\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a n\u1eafm r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 quy tr\u00ecnh nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec follow c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nha!<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: \u0110\u0103ng nh\u1eadp<\/b><\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o website <\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/thisinh.thitotnghiepthpt.edu.vn\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">http:\/\/thisinh.thitotnghiepthpt.edu.vn<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eadp c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin S\u1ed1 CMND, M\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp, M\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5n n\u00fat \u0110\u0102NG NH\u1eacP<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8096 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/z3726037487155_c8d68d4caf6fbbcd6d82790d201e65df.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: V\u00e0o menu Tra c\u1ee9u k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1eeb menu Tra c\u1ee9u<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8098 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/z3726037487855_70ebd231067a36b0df794ab4f0176038.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 14pt;\"><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Xem k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed7i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 th\u00ed sinh \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 ho\u1eb7c Tr\u01b0\u1ee3t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 th\u00ed sinh tr\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8102 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/z3726037478235_e8949cc20b65c0f05b70913c3f41e671.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 14pt;\"><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed7 th\u00ed sinh c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc. \u0110\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc th\u00ed sinh nh\u1ea5n n\u00fat X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8104 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/z3726037478267_926cf2bd20c0483c9bcb2897f22dbd3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 14pt;\"><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Nh\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8106 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/z3726037477566_03799fde4893009ea34209ff2c7557dd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 14pt;\"><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: Ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u0110\u00e3 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8108 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/z3726037466004_66ab0bfea85ebc25a82ece3dad7ed503.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a th\u00ed sinh \u201c\u0110\u00e3 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc\u201d ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 th\u00ed sinh \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a th\u00ed sinh. Khi \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc xong, th\u00ed sinh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u1ee7y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n H\u1ee7y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8110 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/z3726037487205_a54a1be1b96946b99874e58b31f6327b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a th\u00ed sinh \u201c\u0110\u00e3 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc\u201d ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 th\u00ed sinh \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a th\u00ed sinh. Khi \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc xong, th\u00ed sinh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u1ee7y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n H\u1ee7y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng gia nh\u1eadp ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 chung TDD b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u0111ang ch\u1edd c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 nha.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin th\u1eafc m\u1eafc vui l\u00f2ng g\u1eedi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9:<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9: Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Hotline: 0934 07 8668 \u2013 0243 386 1601<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Website: <a href=\"http:\/\/nhaphoc.thanhdo.edu.vn\">http:\/\/nhaphoc.thanhdo.edu.vn<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 4